Wesizwe to Post Profit For 12 Months to Dec. 31, Up From Loss Year Earlier

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-22T15:20:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/wesizwe-to-post-profit-for-12-months-to-dec-31-up-from-loss-year-earlier.html
Wesizwe (WEZ)  Platinum Ltd. said basic
earnings per share attributable to ordinary shareholders for the
12 months to Dec. 31 are expected to be between 39 South African
cents and 42 cents, compared with a basic loss per share of 6.65
cents a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  